sources.title: Tio Papi (Full Movie) bachelor guardian of sister's six kids
sources.description:
Wild bachelor Ray Ray Dominguez dreams of nothing more than a carefree life of indulgence in Miami, but his plans are abruptly changed when he becomes the legal guardian of his sister's six children.  rated PG

Directed by Fro Rojas
2013
Starring Joey Dedio, Kelly McGillis (Top Gun), Frankie Faison (Silence of the Lambs), Elizabeth Rodriguez (Logan)
